name: Fancy-jslint
body:
#Fancy JS Lint

### alpha version
* adds number of warnings below JSLint button
* warns of var in for loop that breaks processing

[click to install in chrome](https://github.com/p4ul/Fancy-JSLint/raw/master/fancyjslint.user.js)

Suggestions encouraged!

### Authors and Contributors
Created by Paul Sinclair (@p4ul)
tagline: Make JSLint a little bit easier to use
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
